column99:
Rays Chicken, an upcoming concept opening in Nordvest Copenhagen, is looking for the right candidate to manage the kitchen. 
 Duties include: 
 
 Chicken butchery and prep. 
 Ordering for the kitchen. 
 Maintaining hygeine through Egen Kontrol, labelling and check lists. 
 Quality control of food production. 
 Keep budgets. 
 Working with FOH staff to ensure a smooth service. 
 
 Schedule is Wednesday to Saturday, 12 to 21 
 Pay is based on experience. 
 Please apply with a CV and cover letter via email.
